@{PAR}@{FG HIGHLIGHT}@{B}¹Bitmap@{UB}@{FG TEXT}@{LINE}
@{PAR}@{B}Create a bitmap of a specified size and color.@{UB}@{LINE}
@{PAR}Produces a portable bitmap of the specified color, width, and height.
The Grey color gives a simple 50% gray pattern with 1's and 0's alternating.@{LINE}
